These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
City: colone, hannover, paris, venice
4 different pets are kept: horse, bird, rat, goldfish
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
2. the person traveling to hannover is not the owner of the horse##6
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
5. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
6. the owner of the horse is not the person traveling to paris##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | hannover   | venice    | colone    | paris |
| Sport      | goldfish | horse | rat | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, rock-climbing, sudoku, magic-tricks
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, monopoly, billiard
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
3. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person playing scrabble##6
5. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | rock-climbing  | sudoku    | dancing | magic-tricks    |
| Food       | billiard | scrabble | monopoly  | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
House: tower, craftsman, wooden, gothic-revival
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, train, taxi, snowmobile
1. the gothic-revival house is not the person driving the airplane##6
2. the person driving the train is not the wooden house##6
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
4. the person driving the train is the tower house##1
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the person driving the train##1
6. the tower house is in an odd position##4
7. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | gothic-revival       | craftsman  | tower  | wooden |
| Job        | taxi | snowmobile | train | airplane  |

