.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
House: ranch-style, futuristic, gothic-revival, colonial
City: edinburgh, marseilles, boston, london
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the colonial house##1
2. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
3. the person traveling to london is not the futuristic house##6
4. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | futuristic | gothic-revival | colonial     | ranch-style |
| Transport   | marseilles     | boston    | edinburgh | london    |

