.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, november, july, december
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, brazilian, thai, australian
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
3. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
4. the person who's birthday is in november is not the australian##6
5. the turkish is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
7. the thai is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | march        | december | july | november |
| Transport   | australian | turkish | brazilian     | thai   |

