.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, september, november
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, techno, hip-hop, pop
1. the fan soul is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is not the fan techno##6
3. the fan soul is on the far right##1
4. the fan techno is somewhere to the right of the fan pop##5
5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the fan soul##5
7. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
8. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the fan pop##5
9. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the fan pop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | may | september    | july  | november   |
| Nationality   | hip-hop  | pop | techno | soul |

