3. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who growsbegonia##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | november | june     | august | july |
| Music-Genre   | bellflower | begonia | zinnia      | azalea         |

