.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, bongani, prince, bolivar
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, gospel, techno, hip-hop
1. the fan folk is on the left of the fan gospel##1
2. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan techno##5
3. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the fan gospel##1
4. the fan gospel is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
5. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the fan gospel##3
6. the fan folk is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
7. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
8. the bongani-smoker is not the fan hip-hop##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | bongani  | alhambra        | prince      | bolivar          |
| Job        | folk | gospel | hip-hop | techno |

