.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, pony, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, climbing, biathlon, swimming
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
2. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the owner of the pony##6
4. the owner of the lizard is between the person who's sport is swimming and the owner of the pony##2
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is badminton and the owner of the chinchilla##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | pony | lizard    | chinchilla | goldfish |
| Music-Genre   | badminton         | climbing | swimming   | biathlon     |

