3. the person who's birthday is in december is the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is not the old-henry-smoker##6
6. the aristoff-smoker is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
7. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the aristoff-smoker##5
8. the blend-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
