3. the person drinking mirinda is the egyptian##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
5. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking coffee and the indian##2
6. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | almond-milk | coffee      | mirinda | hot-chocolate   |
| Movie-Genre   | japanese     | american | egyptian   | indian |

