6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
8. the person eating potato is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
