.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, hiking, reading, rock-climbing
There 4 different types of food: lime, pineapple, carrot, asparagus
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
3. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
4. the person eating lime is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
6. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | video-games | hiking | rock-climbing      | reading   |
| Transport   | asparagus  | pineapple   | carrot | lime |

 